            <p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
            <h2>Other Works Cited </h2>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <p>Alexander, Ronelle.  1985. <em>The Structure of Vasko Popa&rsquo;s  Poetry</em>. Columbus, Slavica.</p>
            <p>Burns Richard. 2004. <em>U vreme su&scaron;e</em> (tr. Vera V. Radojevi&#263;). Belgrade: RAD. </p>
